                  "text": "Exit"
                }
              ],
              "dialogueType": "sendAcceptDecline",
              "text": "The #o1210102#s that have been affected by the noise have turned cynical. They've started fighting the non-affected #o1210102#s, which has made all #o1210102#s prepare for combat. #bThe reason for all these changes in the #o1210102#s is this puppet#k! Do you understand?"
